description:
This is a 21 minute workout called 'Runner's Program #1 of 9' from the channel Peter Donohoe.
The workout falls under Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Progression Quest and The Rhythmic Powerhouse vibe.
The The Progression Quest vibe means Methodical, incremental, long-term improvement. This is especially good for Anyone who loves tracking progress and leveling up. The The Rhythmic Powerhouse vibe means Beat-driven, strong but fluid, music-infused. This is especially good for When you want strength and rhythm to blend seamlessly..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: Start with mobility and functional movement for runners and then incorporate strength building exercises as Pete shares his accomplishments and training. ...
